item.title: Mostra de profissões 2017
item.description: Autobotz was in the Mostra de Profissões 2017 UFMG. The members prepared robots and other Autobot’s experiments to arouse the interest of highschool students in engineering and science. The exposition lasted the whole day and students were able to interact with the projects and talk with the team.
